{
  "texts": [
    "However, additional steps are taken to incorporate the change.",
    "The round function performs successive operations: MixColumns, PermuteCells, AddTweakey, Ad-dConstant, and SubCells.",
    "MANTIS resists truncated differential cryptanalysis with a probability of 2-67.73.",
    "A practical key recovery attack was successful on MANTIS for 228 chosen plaintext with a complexity of 238 [71].",
    "MANTIS is very similar to the Midori block cipher."
